def module R
def desc Press "R" for suicide anchor

on key_press R if targeting_block !if target_block #air switch #anchor then input right then wait 0.05 then switch :glowstone then input right then wait 0.05 switch #totem then wait 0.02 then input right
on tick if holding #glowstone_dust wait 0.05 then switch #glowstone